## 9. Functional Requirements

### 9.1 Dashboard

* Show system health
* Surface exceptions (failed payments, top-ups)
* No editing actions

---

### 9.2 Workers

* Create/edit worker profiles
* Assign skills and locations
* Activate/deactivate workers
* View work summary

**Constraints**

* No document dependency
* No deletion (only deactivation)

---

### 9.3 Jobs

* Create jobs with rates and requirements
* Assign workers
* Track status
* Close jobs explicitly

**Constraints**

* Jobs immutable after closure
* No silent reassignment

---

### 9.4 Income Guarantee

* Define minimum income rules
* Apply at job or global level
* Calculate top-ups deterministically

**Constraints**

* Rules apply forward only
* All applications logged

---

### 9.5 Payments

* Review payable workers
* Trigger batch payouts
* Retry failures
* View transaction references

**Constraints**

* Payments immutable
* Manual override required for retries

---

### 9.6 Work History (Ledger)

* Auto-generated
* Immutable
* Per worker and per job views

**Constraints**

* No edits
* No deletions
* Append-only

---

### 9.7 Reports

* Daily summaries
* Worker earnings
* Top-up usage
* Export (CSV)

---

## 10. User Flows (High Level)

### Worker Flow

Create → Assign → Work → Paid → Logged

### Job Flow

Create → Assign → Complete → Pay → Lock

### Payment Flow

Calculate → Review → Execute → Reconcile → Lock

