## 11. UX & Interaction Requirements

### Layout

* Fixed sidebar
* Sticky top bar
* 12-column grid
* High data density

### Interaction

* Keyboard usable
* Explicit save actions
* Inline validation
* Confirmation on destructive actions

### Prohibited

* Centered layouts
* Hidden saves
* Playful animations
* Auto-advancing flows

---

